OL,3,CMan, 92, charged with murdering 87-
OL,4,Cyear-old woman
OL,6,FA 92-year-old man has been charged
OL,7,Fwith murdering an 87-year-old woman in
OL,8,FExeter.
OL,10,FEmergency services were called to an
OL,11,Faddress on Millbrook Lane at around
OL,12,F12.40pm on Sunday 19 April, following
OL,13,Freports of a concern for welfare.
OL,15,FShirley Billam, 87, died at the scene.
OL,16,FLaurence Billam, of Millbrook Lane,
OL,17,FExeter, has been charged with murder
OL,18,Fand will appear at Exeter Magistrates'
OL,19,FCourt on Tuesday 28 April.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
