OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FDevon and Cornwall Police said Ms
OL,12,FBillam's family are being supported by
OL,13,Fspecially trained officers.
OL,15,FA spokesman for the force said:
OL,16,F"Officers were called to Millbrook
OL,17,FLane at around 12.40pm on Sunday 19
OL,18,FApril following reports of a concern
OL,19,Ffor welfare.
