PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1777374175
OL,3,CMan, 92, charged with murdering 87-
OL,4,Cyear-old woman
OL,6,F"Emergency services attended where a
OL,7,Fwoman was discovered deceased at the
OL,8,Fproperty.
OL,10,F"The woman has since been named as
OL,11,FShirley Billam.
OL,13,F"Laurence Billam, aged 92 and of
OL,14,FMillbrook Lane, Exeter, has been
OL,15,Fcharged with her murder and will
OL,16,Fappear at Exeter Magistrates' Court
OL,17,Fthis morning."
